name: Pastamania?
hintText: Within 2.7km, the mouse can shop till she drops. / The mouse can grab a plate of pasta at the place where she shops.
hintInterpret: Location is 2.7km within a pastamania. Possibly special attention to Orchard Gateway. GPS data taken from postal codes of outlets and 2.7km was accurately plotted. #HAILCORPORATE

name: Trains
hintText: ~ a train can't be heard. (newton mrt hint)
hintInterpret: Location is not near (more than 200m?) from a (overground) MRT track. GPS data taken from https://data.gov.sg/dataset/master-plan-2014-rail-line, 50k data points extracted, shrunk dataset to 2k using math, plotted 2k circles and then reduced to 500-vertice polygon. (trust me your phone would lag if i tried to to it 100% accurate)

name: Location Drop #1
hintText: The mouse is not at River Valley, Bukit Panjang, and Tengah.
hintInterpret: Location is not in these towns. Data obtained from https://docs.onemap.sg/#planning-area-beta.
